actionConfiguration.body:
UPDATE product_register SET
		register_id = '{{update_form.fieldState.register_id.isVisible ? update_form.formData.register_id : update_form.sourceData.register_id}}',
		block_id = '{{update_form.fieldState.block_id.isVisible ? update_form.formData.block_id : update_form.sourceData.block_id}}',
    register_type = '{{update_form.fieldState.register_type.isVisible ? update_form.formData.register_type : update_form.sourceData.register_type}}',
		register_cert_number = '{{update_form.fieldState.register_cert_number.isVisible ? update_form.formData.register_cert_number : update_form.sourceData.register_cert_number}}',
		register_certificate_url = '{{update_form.fieldState.register_certificate_url.isVisible ? update_form.formData.register_certificate_url : update_form.sourceData.register_certificate_url}}',
		register_certificate_img_url = '{{update_form.fieldState.register_certificate_img_url.isVisible ? update_form.formData.register_certificate_img_url : update_form.sourceData.register_certificate_img_url}}',
		register_build_status = '{{update_form.fieldState.register_build_status.isVisible ? update_form.formData.register_build_status : update_form.sourceData.register_build_status}}',
		copyright_ids = '{{update_form.fieldState.copyright_ids.isVisible ? update_form.formData.copyright_ids : update_form.sourceData.copyright_ids}}',
		authors_names = '{{update_form.fieldState.authors_names.isVisible ? update_form.formData.authors_names : update_form.sourceData.authors_names}}',
		auth_ids = '{{update_form.fieldState.auth_ids.isVisible ? update_form.formData.auth_ids : update_form.sourceData.auth_ids}}',
		authors_idcards = '{{update_form.fieldState.authors_idcards.isVisible ? update_form.formData.authors_idcards : update_form.sourceData.authors_idcards}}'
  WHERE register_id = {{data_table.selectedRow.register_id}};
